{"tid":610000,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"真相大白! 一早講左連狗係仆街","createTime":"2018-03-29T13:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T16:00:08.000Z","uid":33125,"like":16,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9670e5efc5a7929510b604280d0945c7438317f6","tid":610000,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:43:16.000Z","msg":"當年予「HKG+」作為第三方手機App，已訂立條款，包括「HKG+」不得暫存網頁內容，以及不可自行賣廣告。不過「HKG+」早於超過半年前已被發現違反承諾，其後高登已向其作警告。至一個月前，「HKG+」再被發現私自暫存網頁內容，「你都知我哋成日收律師信，變咗有啲人以為佢係我哋，封信就畀咗我哋。因為佢哋暫存我哋啲內容，我哋鏟咗就喺佢度出現返。」因此決定停止與「HKG+」合作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他表示，當時「HKG+」表示希望予一個月時間寬限，以向付費VIP用戶負責，「完全冇估到，原來呢個時間係籌備呢樣嘢（LIHKG）。」"},{"pid":"d0d31a066f209f3abd0b8cf825a3a207cb3e3383","tid":610000,"uid":33125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾波台 正經野唔理"},{"pid":"4c719126738474c10067ebf45c94a3e8017c3b6c","tid":610000,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:03:15.000Z","msg":"波台廢青呢?"},{"pid":"86eb7e1d73fc2f90f9bf0a23334a6cd62a25c512","tid":610000,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23db7edb82b6b7df29c93df3b26db1cd31a30caa","tid":610000,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:03:58.000Z","msg":"使你講咩"},{"pid":"c908206de7d2325edae3afd67b6016962ad38c0a","tid":610000,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:10:29.000Z","msg":"但technically 點樣先可以唔暫存？<br />\n<br />\n個app直接連返落高登？<br />\n<br />\n就算過落cache，咪又係暫存，OK個cache秒秒清，即係每次個HKG+存取又要向高登request過data<br />\n<br />\n你高登load得好撚快呀？到時咪又會話request overflow<br />\n<br />\n點解決？"},{"pid":"9c09e90e54b8028111263f480b398ef306ced1c1","tid":610000,"uid":33125,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>使你講咩</b